    {
      "instruction": "<p>Cut the <strong>avocado<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong> in half lengthways, around the stone<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></p><p>Remove the stone<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span> using a teaspoon</p><p>Scoop the <strong>avocado</strong> out of the skin<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span> using a spoon</p><p>Add the <strong>avocado</strong> to a bowl and mash it with a fork</p><p>Season with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong>, add 2 tbsp <span class=\"text-danger\">[4 tbsp] </span><strong>cold water</strong> and squeeze in the juice of 1/2 <span class=\"text-danger\">[1] </span><strong>lime </strong>– this is your <strong>guacamole</strong></p>",
      "order": 2,
