      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Wash and chop the<strong> lettuce </strong>roughly, then pat it dry with<strong> kitchen paper</strong></p><p>Dice the<strong> tomato<span class=\"text-danger\">[es]</span></strong></p><p>Chop the <strong>coconut flakes</strong> finely</p>",
      "order": 3,
