        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Drain, then pat the<strong> jumbo prawns</strong> dry with<strong> kitchen paper</strong></p><p>Add a handful of <strong>flour</strong> to a bowl</p><p>Crack the <strong>egg<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong> into a separate bowl and beat with a fork</p><p>Combine the <strong>panko breadcrumbs</strong> and<strong> chopped coconut flakes </strong>in another bowl – these are your <strong>coconut breadcrumbs</strong></p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
