    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>To serve, pile the<strong> warmed tortillas </strong>with the <strong>guacamole</strong>, <strong>chopped lettuce</strong>, <strong>diced</strong> <strong>tomato</strong> and the <strong>crispy coconut jumbo prawns</strong></p><p>Top with the <strong>pickled chilli </strong>(can't handle the heat? Go easy!) and garnish with a <strong>lime wedge</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
